# === Go ===
# Compiled binaries / build output
*.exe
*.exe~
*.dll
*.so
*.dylib
/telerad-core
/telerad-core-module
bin/
dist/

# Delve / IDE debug binaries
__debug_bin
__debug_bin*
debug
*.test
*.out

# Go workspace / vendor (uncomment vendor/ if you don't vendor deps)
go.work
go.work.sum
# vendor/

# Test & coverage artifacts
coverage.*
*.cover
profile.out

# === Secrets / config ===
# Local environment files (committed example only, if any: .env.example)
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
# .env.railway holds ONLY non-secret fallback config and is baked into the
# Railway image (Dockerfile.railway COPYs it as /app/.env) — must be committed.
!.env.railway

# Cryptographic keys (RS256 JWT keys are embedded via .env in deployment)
*.pem
*.pub
*.key
private_key_*
public_key_*

# === Logs ===
*.log

# === Editor / OS ===
.vscode/
.idea/
*.iml
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
